verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Face to face I shall behold Him,
Far beyond the starry sky;
Face to face in all His glory,
I shall see Him by and by!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}What rejoicing in His presence,
When are banished grief and pain;
When the crooked ways are straightened,
And the dark things shall be plain.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Face to face! O blissful moment!
face to face- to see and know;
face to face with my Redeemer,
Jesus Christ who loves me so.{/lang-eng}
